      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHEEKY SLOY (3) pinged the lids from out wide but faded out of it late when 6th at this track in a Mix 2/3. Can make amends. WICKED RAVEN (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (18.45) at this track behind Lucy Valentine in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Yet to miss the placings from six starts out of this box. Will give a great sight again. QUEEN JEWEL (2) pinged the lids and was in the firing line early but drifted out of it when 6th at this track in Grade 3/4 company. Has ability and can measure up. BOBBY JUNIOR (8) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
